data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Allred Ranch. This beautiful single-level residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty. With its prime location backing to a serene green belt, this home is a rare gem. This home features 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 well-appointed bathrooms, providing ample space for your family's needs Retreat to the master bathroom, where you'll find a luxurious garden tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Enjoy the comfort of a North-South exposure, which helps keep your home cool in the summer, warm in the winter. Stay comfortable all year with the multi-zone AC system, allowing you to customize the climate in different areas of the home to your liking. Don't miss your chance to make this fantastic property your forever home.
